Ideal 61-763 TightSight Clamp Meter - 660 AAC w/TRMS

The new feature-rich Ideal TightSight Clamp Meters are built to professional quality standards to withstand tough use in commercial and industrial settings. The High Frequency Rejection (HFR) feature measures accurately even in noisy electrical environments. For everything from load measurement to troubleshooting industrial motors and adjustable speed drives (ASDs), the new TightSight Clamps bring speed, accuracy, safety and ease-of-use together in one rugged meter. Includes batteries.

Ideal Industries TightSight(TM) 760 Series Digital clamp meter with TRMS, measures AC current of 0 - 660-Amps, AC input voltage of 0 - 750-Volts and DC input voltage of 0 - 999.9-Volts. It has backlit LCD display features large numbers and green glowing backlight. This clamp meter works on 9-Volt battery. It is suitable to measure 20 - 400-Hz frequency, 0 - 999.9 mF capacitance and 0 - 9999-Ohm resistance. This clamp meter measures temperature in range of 0 to 50 deg C. It has unique TightSight(TM) bottom display that makes hard-to-reach measurements easy. This clamp meter has tapered jaws with hook tip. It is suitable for various industrial and commercial environments. Clamp meter is UL listed and CE certified.
